4
00:00:24,474 --> 00:00:25,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini aku, cowok gang.</font>

5
00:00:26,043 --> 00:00:27,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Cowok gang?</font>

6
00:00:28,311 --> 00:00:31,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, cowok gang yang kutemui
waktu aku lagi mencari Bok Nam.</font>

7
00:00:31,214 --> 00:00:32,540
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ya, si Bok Nam.</i></font>

8
00:00:33,583 --> 00:00:34,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, ada apa?</font>

9
00:00:34,918 --> 00:00:36,580
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ada yang ingin kutanyakan padamu.</i></font>

10
00:00:36,853 --> 00:00:38,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ada kertas di sampingmu?</i>/
Kertas?</font>

11
00:00:40,090 --> 00:00:41,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ada.</font>

12
00:00:42,359 --> 00:00:43,560
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pena, ada?</i></font>

13
00:00:44,594 --> 00:00:45,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Pena juga, ada.</font>

14
00:00:45,662 --> 00:00:47,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kalau pacar?/</i>
Pacar...</font>

15
00:00:49,966 --> 00:00:52,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?/
<i>Pacar juga, kau punya?</i></font>

16
00:01:01,711 --> 00:01:03,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau pacar...,</font>

17
00:01:07,717 --> 00:01:10,520
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku tak punya.</font>

18
00:01:18,595 --> 00:01:19,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku permisi dulu.</font>

19
00:01:32,175 --> 00:01:34,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kenapa kau tanya itu ke aku?</font>

20
00:01:35,078 --> 00:01:37,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lihat Bok Nam di gang.</font>

21
00:01:37,447 --> 00:01:38,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia berjalan sendirian lagi.</font>

22
00:01:39,216 --> 00:01:42,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Serius? Si Bok Nam
kabur dari rumah lagi?</font>

23
00:01:46,056 --> 00:01:47,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi...</font>

24
00:01:48,291 --> 00:01:50,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tidak ada hubungannya
denganku sekarang.</font>

25
00:01:51,862 --> 00:01:53,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Lagipula kafe itu pasti sudah
dapat pekerja sambilan yang baru.</font>

26
00:01:55,732 --> 00:01:57,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa harus kuberitahu nama
kafenya?</font>

27
00:01:57,501 --> 00:01:59,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa langsung menghubungi mereka.</font>

28
00:01:59,336 --> 00:02:00,800
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Gang yang sama waktu
kita bertemu kemarin.</i></font>

29
00:02:00,937 --> 00:02:03,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?/
Datanglah ke sana jam setengah 12 siang.</font>

30
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:05,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat itu, carilah si Bok Nam.</font>

31
00:02:06,343 --> 00:02:08,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo? Tapi kenapa aku harus...</font>

32
00:02:08,945 --> 00:02:10,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo?</font>

33
00:02:19,156 --> 00:02:20,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Jam berapa tadi dia bilang?</font>

34
00:02:21,124 --> 00:02:22,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Jam sebelas?</font>

35
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, jam setengah 12.</font>

36
00:02:31,968 --> 00:02:34,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Anjing itu 'kan sendirian.</font>

37
00:02:36,673 --> 00:02:39,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, ini karena aku tidak punya pekerjaan.</font>

38
00:02:39,776 --> 00:02:41,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku punya banyak waktu luang.</font>

39
00:02:44,114 --> 00:02:47,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Kau saja selalu tidur siang.</font>

40
00:02:48,652 --> 00:02:49,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

41
00:03:08,705 --> 00:03:10,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Apa dia ini selebriti?</i></font>

42
00:03:10,774 --> 00:03:13,040
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia tampan sekali.</i></font>

43
00:03:14,277 --> 00:03:15,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa ini?</font>

44
00:03:15,312 --> 00:03:17,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami tengah menyaring profil...,</font>

45
00:03:17,347 --> 00:03:19,980
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan ada anggota terkeren
yang baru mendaftar.</font>

46
00:03:21,651 --> 00:03:23,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Daebak. Dia dapat nilai tertinggi.</font>

47
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku iri sekali./
Dia berhasil.</font>

48
00:03:26,356 --> 00:03:28,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah itu skor tertinggi
yang kita miliki sejauh ini?</font>

49
00:03:28,925 --> 00:03:30,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Anggota yang daftar aplikasi
kita paling tinggi cuma dapat sembilan.</font>

50
00:03:30,694 --> 00:03:32,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Betul./ Dia orang pertama
yang dapat nilai tertinggi.</font>

51
00:03:32,729 --> 00:03:36,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini artinya dia tipe orang yang
disukai anak muda belakangan ini.</font>

52
00:03:36,499 --> 00:03:38,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia seperti anak anjing./
Ya, betul.</font>

53
00:03:40,604 --> 00:03:42,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa umurnya?/
24.</font>

54
00:03:42,872 --> 00:03:45,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Berarti aku dua tahun lebih tua.</font>

55
00:03:45,642 --> 00:03:48,270
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Skor Diamond: 9.18]</i></font>

56
00:03:54,884 --> 00:03:56,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu!/
Ayah.</font>

57
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:59,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanya kenapa kau pasang wajah
jelek begitu? Buat kaget orang saja.</font>

58
00:04:00,457 --> 00:04:01,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sendiri juga.</font>

59
00:04:03,326 --> 00:04:04,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Bok Nam-nya mana?</font>

60
00:04:05,562 --> 00:04:06,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Ikut aku.</font>

61
00:04:13,003 --> 00:04:14,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu...</font>

62
00:04:15,071 --> 00:04:17,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kita masuk ke sana?
Bok Nam-nya mana?</font>

63
00:04:18,108 --> 00:04:19,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuklah dulu, supaya
kita bisa menemukannya.</font>

64
00:04:20,176 --> 00:04:21,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

65
00:04:22,712 --> 00:04:24,710
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa masuk sini.</font>

66
00:04:25,148 --> 00:04:27,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku gagal melamar
kerja sambilan disini.</font>

67
00:04:27,317 --> 00:04:28,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

68
00:04:28,752 --> 00:04:32,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah pemiliknya menyuruhmu
mencari si Bok Nam?</font>

69
00:04:32,522 --> 00:04:33,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, makanya.</font>

70
00:04:34,224 --> 00:04:36,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat pertama kali bertemu, aku
disuruh cari anjingnya...,</font>

71
00:04:37,027 --> 00:04:39,960
<font color=#FFFF00>...setelah itu, dia tidak pernah
menghubungiku lagi.</font>

72
00:04:40,697 --> 00:04:42,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Artinya aku gagal dapat pekerjaan itu.</font>

73
00:04:42,165 --> 00:04:43,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi kenapa?</font>

74
00:04:44,134 --> 00:04:46,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana kau bisa gagal,
padahal kau lulusan sarjana?</font>

75
00:04:48,638 --> 00:04:50,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tentu bisa gagal...</font>

76
00:04:50,707 --> 00:04:53,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa jadi karena umurku
atau kurangnya pengalamanku.</font>

77
00:04:54,110 --> 00:04:57,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Bos kafe ini mungkin
merasa tidak nyaman.</font>

78
00:04:57,347 --> 00:04:58,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak nyaman apaan.</font>

79
00:04:58,748 --> 00:05:00,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Merasa tidak nyaman denganmu
karena apa, coba?</font>

80
00:05:00,784 --> 00:05:02,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Dari sekali lihat saja, kau
pasti orang yang mudah disuruh-suruh.</font>

81
00:05:02,886 --> 00:05:04,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa-bisanya dia tidak menerimamu?</font>

82
00:05:04,854 --> 00:05:06,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia itu memang tak bakat
mempekerjakan orang.</font>

83
00:05:07,357 --> 00:05:10,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ini pujian?</font>

84
00:05:10,327 --> 00:05:11,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya lah.</font>

85
00:05:11,661 --> 00:05:14,060
<font color=#FFFF00>kau bekerja keras hari ini
karena Bok Nam lagi.</font>

86
00:05:14,831 --> 00:05:16,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Bos kafe ini memang mengerikan.</font>

87
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Padahal dia duluan yang menyuruhmu
cari anjingnya.</font>

88
00:05:18,768 --> 00:05:21,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Teganya dia tak menerimamu
jadi pekerja sambilan?</font>

89
00:05:23,673 --> 00:05:24,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo masuk.</font>

90
00:05:24,874 --> 00:05:26,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus mencari tahu kenapa
dia tak menerimamu.</font>

91
00:05:26,976 --> 00:05:28,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku harus masuk?</font>

92
00:05:28,478 --> 00:05:29,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei!</font>

93
00:05:30,313 --> 00:05:32,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu sebentar. Terima kasih.</font>

94
00:05:32,782 --> 00:05:34,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

95
00:05:35,585 --> 00:05:37,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Bok Nam.
Kau ini.</font>

96
00:05:37,487 --> 00:05:39,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ini sibuk. Kemana saja kau?</font>

97
00:05:39,589 --> 00:05:40,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Bok Nam?</font>

98
00:05:41,691 --> 00:05:44,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Makanya aku bawa pekerja
sambilan yang baru.</font>

99
00:05:44,561 --> 00:05:47,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Bok Nam. Aku tidak menyuruhmu
seperti ini.</font>

100
00:05:47,063 --> 00:05:49,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Memang dimana Bok Nam-nya?</font>

101
00:05:53,336 --> 00:05:55,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan kujadikan asistenku
mulai besok.</font>

102
00:05:55,438 --> 00:05:57,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, Yeon Bok Nam, kau...</font>

103
00:05:58,641 --> 00:06:00,740
<font color=#FFFF00>"Bok Nam"...</font>

104
00:06:02,278 --> 00:06:04,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Rambutnya cokelat berbulu.</font>

105
00:06:05,215 --> 00:06:06,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Merah muda.</font>

106
00:06:07,283 --> 00:06:09,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi Bok Nam itu orang?</font>

107
00:06:12,455 --> 00:06:15,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika dia tidak dipekerjakan disini,
aku akan mengundurkan diri.</font>

108
00:06:15,058 --> 00:06:16,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?/
Apa?</font>

109
00:06:25,235 --> 00:06:27,870
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tadinya mau meneleponmu...,</font>

110
00:06:27,871 --> 00:06:30,200
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi toko lagi sibuk sekali.</font>

111
00:06:30,206 --> 00:06:31,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya./
Ya.</font>

112
00:06:33,743 --> 00:06:37,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, apa kebetulan menurut
Bapak aku kurang cocok bekerja disini...</font>

113
00:06:37,414 --> 00:06:40,610
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi Bapak terpaksa menerimaku
karena si Bok Nam?</font>

114
00:06:40,617 --> 00:06:43,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak. Asal Bok Nam menyukaimu,
aku tak apa.</font>

115
00:06:43,987 --> 00:06:45,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang harus menyukai rekan mereka.</font>

116
00:06:45,722 --> 00:06:48,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu, sampai ketemu besok.</font>

117
00:06:48,124 --> 00:06:50,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Terima kasih.</font>

118
00:07:09,979 --> 00:07:11,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

119
00:07:12,115 --> 00:07:13,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sudah diterima kerja disini?</font>

120
00:07:14,784 --> 00:07:16,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya./
Baguslah.</font>

121
00:07:18,455 --> 00:07:21,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau begini padaku?</font>

122
00:07:21,858 --> 00:07:24,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Begini apa?/
Apa?</font>

123
00:07:24,794 --> 00:07:25,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Maksudnya, aku menghubungimu?</font>

124
00:07:25,962 --> 00:07:27,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau tidak memberitahu namaku?</font>

125
00:07:27,664 --> 00:07:30,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Atau soal mencarikanmu pekerjaan?
Yang mana yang kaumaksud?</font>

126
00:07:34,904 --> 00:07:37,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Yah... tiga-tiganya.</font>

127
00:07:38,308 --> 00:07:40,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Bok Nam! Kirim pesanannya...</font>

128
00:07:40,743 --> 00:07:42,040
<font color=#FFFF00>...sekarang juga./
Ya.</font>

129
00:07:47,650 --> 00:07:48,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemarilah.</font>

130
00:07:49,786 --> 00:07:50,950
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

131
00:07:50,954 --> 00:07:52,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukannya tadi kau bertanya
padaku?</font>

132
00:07:59,429 --> 00:08:00,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau ini kenapa?</font>

133
00:08:00,830 --> 00:08:02,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku disuruh kirim pesanan.</font>

134
00:08:02,699 --> 00:08:04,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Naiklah. Nanti kujawab pertanyaanmu,
kalau kita sudah sampai.</font>

135
00:08:05,969 --> 00:08:08,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Serius?/
Iya, naiklah dulu.</font>

136
00:08:08,238 --> 00:08:09,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ini sibuk, tahu.</font>

137
00:08:12,942 --> 00:08:14,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Kimchi-nya enak sekali tadi.</font>

138
00:08:14,944 --> 00:08:17,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus sering-sering
makan siang di luar kantor.</font>

139
00:08:17,146 --> 00:08:18,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Biar sama seperti orang lain.</font>

140
00:08:29,859 --> 00:08:31,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu 'kan istrinya Se Hee.</font>

141
00:08:53,883 --> 00:08:55,680
<font color=#FFFF00>Santai saja.</font>

142
00:08:55,952 --> 00:08:59,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, jawablah. Kenapa
kau melakukannya?</font>

143
00:08:59,622 --> 00:09:02,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya menurutmu kenapa?
Itu karena aku menyukaimu.</font>

144
00:09:03,793 --> 00:09:05,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku?</font>

145
00:09:05,361 --> 00:09:06,620
<font color=#FFFF00>Terus siapa lagi?</font>

146
00:09:08,765 --> 00:09:11,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Pak Yoon. Ya.</font>

147
00:09:11,167 --> 00:09:13,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah dekat.
Boleh aku datang sekarang?</font>

148
00:09:13,436 --> 00:09:15,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

149
00:09:16,339 --> 00:09:18,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai besok./
Hei.</font>

150
00:09:20,343 --> 00:09:22,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa aku membuatmu
jadi salah paham.</font>

151
00:09:22,912 --> 00:09:25,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Pacar, memang aku tak punya...,</font>

152
00:09:27,417 --> 00:09:28,780
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku punya suami.</font>

153
00:09:38,628 --> 00:09:41,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Pasti dia adiknya.</font>

154
00:09:41,197 --> 00:09:42,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka kelihatan mirip.</font>

155
00:09:42,865 --> 00:09:46,043
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu? 'Kan kita sudah
pernah lihat adiknya di pesta pernikahan.</font>

156
00:09:52,275 --> 00:09:54,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Terus kenapa?/
Apa?</font>

157
00:09:54,844 --> 00:09:57,580
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau punya suami, terus
aku bisa apa.</font>

158
00:09:59,415 --> 00:10:02,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau kau punya suami,
kau tak boleh punya pacar?</font>

159
00:10:11,728 --> 00:10:15,330
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Episode 6: Karena ini *YOLO Pertamaku]</i>
(You Only Live Once=Hidup Hanya Sekali)</font>

160
00:10:19,268 --> 00:10:20,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang apa?</font>

161
00:10:20,303 --> 00:10:22,270
<font color=#FFFF00>"Kalau kau punya suami,
kau tak boleh punya pacar?"</font>

162
00:10:23,606 --> 00:10:25,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Terus habis itu, kau bilang apa?</font>

163
00:10:25,642 --> 00:10:28,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada. Aku terlalu tertegun
mau balas ucapan dia.</font>

164
00:10:29,112 --> 00:10:31,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Anak-anak zaman sekarang
memang begitu berani.</font>

165
00:10:33,349 --> 00:10:34,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa umurnya? 24?</font>

166
00:10:34,484 --> 00:10:36,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. 24 tahun.</font>

167
00:10:36,853 --> 00:10:39,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisa-bisanya dia main-main
denganku?</font>

168
00:10:41,958 --> 00:10:44,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Soo Ji, bekerja keraslah
menekuni pekerjaanmu.</font>

169
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:46,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Walau sulit, tetaplah bertahan.</font>

170
00:10:49,699 --> 00:10:52,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena aku berhenti menjadi penulis,
aku tak bisa apa-apa lagi.</font>

171
00:10:52,969 --> 00:10:56,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Umurku sudah setengah jalan
menjadi 60, tapi aku bekerja sama pria...</font>

172
00:10:56,205 --> 00:10:58,170
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang lebih muda dari
adikku sendiri, dan aku dikerjai sama dia.</font>

173
00:10:58,374 --> 00:11:01,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Menurutku kau tak boleh bilang begitu
sama aku yang...</font>

174
00:11:01,477 --> 00:11:04,480
<font color=#FFFF00>...selalu dikerjai sama
pria-pria tua tiap hari.</font>

175
00:11:05,214 --> 00:11:06,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

176
00:11:08,351 --> 00:11:11,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Ho Rang mana? Bukannya
restoran tutup hari ini?</font>

177
00:11:12,588 --> 00:11:14,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia lagi uring-uringan sekarang.</font>

178
00:11:14,991 --> 00:11:16,190
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

179
